    {
        "content": "<p>In order to obtain a characterization of (pre)stacks for a precoverage (which satisfies slightly stronger axioms than pretopologies), I had to refactor <a href=\"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/pull/33179\">#33179</a> (which <span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"519559\">@Dagur Asgeirsson</span> had already maintainer delegated) and add the prerequisite PR <a href=\"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/pull/33287\">#33287</a> about sieves and sheaves on <code>Over</code> categories; I am sorry for the extra work...</p>",
